25/01/2025_ringo-starr_jackwhite_sherylcrow_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_ringo-starr_jackwhite_sherylcrow_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_ringo-starr_jackwhite_sherylcrow_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_ringo-starr_jackwhite_sherylcrow_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_ringo-starr_jackwhite_sherylcrow_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_ringo-starr_jackwhite_sherylcrow_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔 (Ringo Starr)</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-white">杰克·怀特 (Jack White)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sheryl-crow">谢丽尔·克劳</a>(Sheryl Crow) 等人一起参加了一场乡村音乐会，庆祝他的遗产。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-beatles-every-song-ranked-3121214">披头士乐队：每首歌按伟大程度排列</a></strong></li></ul><p>本周早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-announces-special-country-concert-with-jack-white-and-sheryl-crow-3828914">，这部名为“Ringo &amp; Friends At The Ryman”的两小时节目</a>在纳什维尔的莱曼礼堂举行，将于春季在哥伦比亚广播公司 (CBS) 播出，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paramount">派拉蒙+ (Paramount+)</a>上播出。</p><p>斯塔尔通过乡村镜头表演了他最近的乡村专辑《Look Up》中的歌曲以及他的独奏热门歌曲和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Beatles">披头士乐队的</a>经典歌曲。音乐会的收益将捐献给美国红十字会和受洛杉矶山火影响的人们。</p><p>怀特与斯塔尔一起翻唱了卡尔·珀金斯的《火柴盒》，为演出拉开帷幕，随后他表演了披头士乐队的经典歌曲《Don&#39;t Pass Me By》。您可以查看下面的视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="林戈斯塔尔和朋友在田纳西州纳什维尔莱曼礼堂 01/14/2025" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zn1nWc40u9U?start=252&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin